[{"chinese":"怦然心动","english":"Flipped","year":"2010","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p501177648.jpg","type":"movie","director":"罗伯·莱纳","douban_score":"9.1","my_comment":"青春爱情，祛魅"},{"chinese":"漫长的季节","english":"漫长的季节","year":"2023","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2890906384.jpg","type":"series","director":"辛爽","douban_score":"9.4","my_comment":"国产难得的短剧集，剧情跌宕起伏，每一集都没有注水，故事比较合理"},{"chinese":"小妇人","english":"Little Women","year":"2019","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2572928166.jpg","type":"movie","director":"格蕾塔·葛韦格","douban_score":"8.0","my_comment":"对比原书改变较为成功，两条时空线交替闪回，画面优美，同时其独立自主的思想也引入深思"},{"chinese":"傲慢与偏见","english":"Pride & Prejudice","year":"2005","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2016401659.jpg","type":"movie","director":"乔·赖特","douban_score":"8.7","my_comment":"对于故事情节还原的很不错，达西与伊丽莎白的雨中争吵堪称一绝"},{"chinese":"沉默的真相","english":"沉默的真相","year":"2020","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2620780603.jpg","type":"series","director":"陈奕甫","douban_score":"9.0","my_comment":"改编自紫金陈的长夜难明，悬疑小说，和漫长的季节一样属于国产精品短剧集"},{"chinese":"成为简·奥斯汀","english":"Becoming Jane","year":"2007","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p1284506783.jpg","type":"movie","director":"朱里安·杰拉德","douban_score":"8.3","my_comment":"傲慢与偏见的作者个人生平改编，对于作者本生平改编有些取巧的地方，典型的英式画面风格，和小妇人主题差不多"},{"chinese":"绝命毒师 第一季","english":"Breaking Bad","year":"2008","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2886443948.jpg","type":"series","director":"亚当·伯恩斯坦","douban_score":"9.2","my_comment":"毒师应该算是比较经典的美剧了吧，剧情、画面、拍摄都可以说是典范，为了节省空间，这里就以第一部举例"},{"chinese":"风骚律师 第一季","english":"Better Call Saul","year":"2015","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2218944919.jpg","type":"series","director":"文斯·吉里根","douban_score":"9.3","my_comment":"和毒师同系列的作品，这里讲述了吉米变为Saul的国程，这个的拍摄和画面可以算是影视教材了，和毒师一样，这里只写一部"},{"chinese":"简爱","english":"Jane Eyre","year":"2011","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p1590555816.jpg","type":"movie","director":"凯瑞·福永","douban_score":"7.6","my_comment":"对于小说的还原度并没有那么好，但由于原著不错，因此这个电影推荐给想读但又没有时间读的读者，和小妇人、傲慢与偏见一样，属于女性成长题材，画面也很美"},{"chinese":"海蒂和爷爷","english":"Heidi","year":"2015","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2554525534.jpg","type":"movie","director":"阿兰·葛斯彭纳","douban_score":"9.3","my_comment":"画风不错，挺治愈的"},{"chinese":"赎罪","english":"Atonement","year":"2007","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2174553771.jpg","type":"movie","director":"乔·赖特","douban_score":"8.6","my_comment":"同样的英式画风，但与其说是赎罪，不如说是自我救赎（自我感动）"},{"chinese":"死亡诗社","english":"Dead Poets Society","year":"1989","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2575465690.jpg","type":"movie","director":"彼得·威尔","douban_score":"9.2","my_comment":"Oh captain,my captain! But poetry, beauty, romance, love -- these are what we stay alive for。"},{"chinese":"无耻之徒 第一季","english":"Shameless","year":"2004","poster":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yasingf/blog_cdn/img/p2629522482.jpg","type":"series","director":"保罗·艾伯特","douban_score":"9.0","my_comment":"人生的容错率很大，尽管去做你想做的事情吧，尺度稍微有些大，不建议公共场合播放，不过性爱只是其中的一小部分，电视剧还是很值的一看的，和毒师一样，这里只写第一季"}]